28#include <sys/cdefs.h>
29__KERNEL_RCSID(0, "$NetBSD: nouveau_nvkm_subdev_fb_nv4e.c,v 1.2 2018/08/27 04:58:33 riastradh Exp $");
30
31#include "priv.h"
32#include "ram.h"
33
34static const struct nvkm_fb_func
35nv4e_fb = {
36 .init = nv44_fb_init,
37 .tile.regions = 12,
38 .tile.init = nv46_fb_tile_init,
39 .tile.fini = nv20_fb_tile_fini,
40 .tile.prog = nv44_fb_tile_prog,
41 .ram_new = nv44_ram_new,
42 .memtype_valid = nv04_fb_memtype_valid,
43};
44
45int
46nv4e_fb_new(struct nvkm_device *device, int index, struct nvkm_fb **pfb)
47{
48 return nvkm_fb_new_(&nv4e_fb, device, index, pfb);
49}
